76561197977757903,Recommended,232910,8369221,"Posted: 28 December, 2013",all,T3quila,"For all lovers of Trackmania Nations and it's various flavors, this is a no-brainer. Just get it, you'll love it too. Pretty much the same game with updated graphics, but for under 5$, it's hard to resist.For everybody else: This is a very arcade like racer. The whole fun to be had is online in it's multiplayer mode. The most common play modes involve a rotating track list with a fixed amount of time per track to run your best time. You see all the other players ghosts but won't have any collisions with them. No damage model, unlimited retries and a very fast paced play make this game to an absolute time killer. Everybody has the same car stat-wise so there is no advantages in that regard for anybody and no pay to win scenario. You can customize the skin of your car however you want though. The game's highlight is the track editor. You can build marvelous tracks with banked corners, jumps and loops in no time. A dedicated server is freely available as well as a ladder system. This game once played will make you come back over and over. The famous ""I'll play for 5 minutes"" (which is totally possible) usually turn into 2 hour sessions. ""Just one more round..."". Give it a try, you will not regret it."
