76561198098027635,Recommended,232910,31658999,Posted: 9 May,all,OldsXCool,"WTF! This game was perfect! Then I was forced to do a massive update that promised higher frame rates, lower load times and I got the exact opposite! Now the game has frame pacing issues and the user interface is broken! The load times are about 3 times longer than they used to be! Plus the stupid game barely worked after the update as it told me that there was no game after the update in which I had to restart and re sign in.EDIT: Yes this was an unfavorable review that has turned into to a favorable because these issues have now been fixed after a few more updates. The game runs as good as it looks now and there are no longer any frame pacing issues as it runs smooth as silk like before. The update actually now delivers what it initially promised which was better graphics with higher frame rates. In addition to the fixes, you now don't have to run an official race in the solo campaign to solidify a record which is a massively welcome addition to the game and one that should have been done a long time ago. You used to have to practice for 5 minutes then choose to do an official run in order to set a record. If you didn't happen to race very well you were forced to practice again for 5 minutes until you could go for a record again which was maddening especially if you did well in practice and then F'ed up the official run. Now every run can set a record."
